  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective study enrolling consecutive patients who undergo transurethral
      resection of the bladder tumour (TURBT) aimed at determination of a safety of the procedure.
      Study end-points are incidence, severity and predictive factors of surgical complications.
      The study secondary aim is a validation of Clavien Dindo scoring system for reporting
      complication of TURBT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
